5D201C8E.Line1.B20BA: She was cruel, but effective. Blackweald Company was feared yet respected under her command.

91090F92.Line5.B20BA: Her body remained, but her soul was long extinguished.

F7149610.Line3.B20BA: The Days of Ash changed everything. She was consumed by the horrors we witnessed - and they consumed her, in turn.
